  "2026-06-17T23:56:19.283Z",codex-audit-agent,"Evidence: addressed PR #266 AI review feedback. Existing pm init settings now compute pending changes and require --force before mutating id_prefix/governance_preset/author_default. Dynamic extension commands without declared flags now reject unknown options even when Commander parses --no-* as false, and errors render canonical kebab-case flags. Verification passed: focused init/dynamic/script test set; full coverage 226 files / 4493 tests with 100% statements, branches, functions, and lines."
  "2026-06-18T00:03:01.324Z",codex-audit-agent,"Release-gate evidence: node dist/cli.js changelog generate --check returned unchanged after package-owned changelog generation. pnpm version:check && pnpm contracts:check && pnpm security:scan && pnpm quality:static && npm pack --dry-run passed; contracts snapshot cleanup exercised successfully. Note: pnpm changelog:pm:check wrapper was interrupted because its second pm-changelog install child stalled in npm install @unbrained/pm-cli@>=2026.6.7 after regeneration; direct installed-extension check passed."
